item.title: CVE-2021-38350|2024-08-04T01:37:16.510Z -- spideranalyse -- spideranalyse
item.description: The spideranalyse WordPress plugin is vulnerable to Reflected Cross-Site Scripting via the date parameter found in the ~/analyse/index.php file which allows attackers to inject arbitrary web scripts, in versions up to and including 0.0.1.
